# CODEOWNERS — demonstrates the per-path approval routing pattern.
#
# In the real implementation, replace the placeholder owner (@ffgdeo) with the
# actual GitHub team for each data owner, e.g.:
#   /catalogs/finance_prod/  @procore/data-owners-finance
#   /catalogs/marketing_prod/ @procore/data-owners-marketing
#   /modules/                 @procore/platform-team
#
# For this reference repo to function as a demo, we use a single placeholder
# owner so that auto-assigned reviews resolve to a real user.

# Modules: pattern owners only
/modules/                              @ffgdeo

# Catalogs: data owner of each catalog (one per directory)
/catalogs/                             @ffgdeo

# Groups: data owner of the catalog the group belongs to
/groups/                               @ffgdeo

# Admin groups: platform team only
/admins/                               @ffgdeo

# CODEOWNERS itself: platform team only
/.github/CODEOWNERS                    @ffgdeo
